<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>We Value Your Feedback</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #ffffff;
      margin: 30px auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: #6366F1; /* Indigo-500 */
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background: #10B981; /* Emerald-500 */
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background: #059669; /* Emerald-600 */
    }
    .footer {
      background: #E5E7EB; /* Gray-200 */
      color: #374151; /* Gray-700 */
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #6366F1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Your Feedback is Important!</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Thank you for attending <strong>{{eventName}}</strong>. We hope you had a great experience.</p>
      <p>We would love to hear your thoughts! Please click the button below to let us know how we did.</p>
      <a class="btn" href="{{feedbackUrl}}" target="_blank">Give Feedback</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you once again! If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@example.com">contact us</a>.</p>
      <p>Â© {{year}} PASA. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
